data.description: 4 Bed/ 3 Bath Home in the heart of Port Orange. This is the perfect home for a large families or even roommates who are looking for lots of living space. Split floor plan. Downstairs offers foyer, master with walk-in-closet, guest bedroom, two full bathrooms, kitchen and living/ dining room combo. The upstairs features two more bedrooms, one full bath plus a loft. Kitchen sliders lead to backyard patio. Privacy fence could be added or enjoy the conservation view. Additional features include inside laundry, Hurricane shutters and under stairs storage. Short commute to shopping, beaches, hospitals, schools and major highways.  Seller is will consider replacing roof, AC or water heater before closing if cost is added to purchase price. This Home is being sold ''As Is'' and is ready for your personal touches.
